---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="DID One Identity Platform" description="Identity First World powered by DIDCore.">
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Identity First World</div>
          <h1>DID One Identity Platform</h1>
          <p class="lede">DID One makes identity the first stable object for humans, agents, tools, skills, APIs, devices, organizations, credentials, and worlds.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="button" href="/identity-platform/didcore/">Explore DIDCore</a>
            <a class="button secondary" href="https://github.com/didoneworld/identity-platform">View GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <div class="badge">Platform Law</div>
          <pre class="code-card">No identity, no action.
No proof, no trust.
No lifecycle, no agent.
No recovery, no production identity.</pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>DIDCore is the kernel</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card"><h3>Identity</h3><p>DID, DID Document, controller, verification methods, wallet binding, and credential anchors.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>Governance</h3><p>Lifecycle states, JIT authorization, trust chains, policy gates, and audit events.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>Recovery</h3><p>Every identity and agent must recover, exit gracefully, retire safely, and remain backward verifiable.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container panel">
        <h2>One protocol. Many worlds.</h2>
        <p>DID One starts as the Identity Core World and becomes the base for governance, enterprise, social, commerce, globalization, federation, agentic systems, real-world systems, R&D, excellence, exploration, and multiversal worlds.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
